+# Authentication
+
+## Overview
+
+The API uses token-based authentication with session management.
+
+## Endpoints
+
+- `POST /users` — Create a new user account
+- `POST /login` — Authenticate and receive a session token
+
+## Usage
+
+1. Create a user with `POST /users`
+2. Login with `POST /login` to receive a session token
+3. Include the token in subsequent requests: `Authorization: Bearer <token>`
+
+Sessions expire after 24 hours.
